To assist individuals in effectively communicating their transferable skills and experience to potential employers in a new field, Go code can be used to analyze job descriptions and provide suggestions for how to tailor their resume and cover letter to the specific job requirements.
Here is an example of how Go code can be used to create a career change navigation tool:
