magnitude_a = norm(a);
magnitude_b = norm(b);
angle = acos(dot_product / (magnitude_a * magnitude_b));
angle_degrees = rad2deg(angle);
```
This code snippet calculates the angle between the points (2,3) and (5,7) using the dot product method.
