How can I find a 7-digit number that meets the following criteria: the sum of the first three digits is equal to the sum of the last three digits, and the sum of all seven digits is equal to 42? Also, each digit must be between 1 and 9 (inclusive) and cannot be repeated within the number.
Here is the JavaScript code that I have tried:
